                                  "children": {
                                    "34": {
                                      "id": "34",
                                      "speaker": "Shar",
                                      "text": "Like the Dark Justiciars of old, you must journey to my innermost sanctum and make a sacrifice in my name. You will become my Voice made flesh, to command all who bow to me.",
